WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.286 --> 00:00:10.218
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16.527 --> 00:00:19.189
<i>Running like a fugitive.</i>

3
00:00:20.097 --> 00:00:22.395
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:24.067 --> 00:00:26.729
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27.838 --> 00:00:30.466
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:32.175 --> 00:00:35.269
<i>For no single one.</i>

7
00:00:35.913 --> 00:00:39.041
<i>To none does belong.</i>

8
00:00:40.517 --> 00:00:44.886
<i>This time is ours. right now...</i>

9
00:00:47.524 --> 00:00:49.287
<i>Unraveling the pain.</i>

10
00:00:49.393 --> 00:00:51.122
<i>Unraveling our hearts.</i>

11
00:00:51.194 --> 00:00:53.526
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:55.065 --> 00:00:56.828
<i>Stifling our breath.</i>

13
00:00:56.900 --> 00:00:58.800
<i>Reaching for beyond.</i>

14
00:00:58.869 --> 00:01:01.303
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:03.206 --> 00:01:09.770
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10.881 --> 00:01:13.372
<i>To the distant light above.</i>

17
00:01:14.151 --> 00:01:17.018
<i>Yes. we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21.858 --> 00:01:23.155
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25.629 --> 00:01:27.153
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:32.964 --> 00:01:34.625
<i>The Village Hidden in the Leaves.</i>

21
00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:39.960
<i>This is a Hidden Village that has produced</i>
<i>many superb Ninjas.</i>

22
00:01:40.038 --> 00:01:43.064
- Hey Naruto! Why did you do such a thing?!
- You're really gonna get it this time!

23
00:01:43.141 --> 00:01:46.008
<i>The number one prankster of the village.</i>
<i>Naruto Uzumaki.</i>

24
00:01:46.077 --> 00:01:48.807
<i>is a boy who is also</i>
<i>striving to become a first rate Ninja.</i>

25
00:01:49.247 --> 00:01:51.010
I don't care!

26
00:01:53.251 --> 00:01:54.445
Transform!

27
00:01:55.954 --> 00:01:59.185
<i>His strongest skill is the Sexy Jutsu.</i>

28
00:01:59.691 --> 00:02:02.125
- You fool!
- <i>However. Naruto had a secret inside him.</i>

29
00:02:02.193 --> 00:02:03.990
- Stop making idiotic spells!
- <i>that even he didn't know about.</i>

30
00:02:06.297 --> 00:02:10.393
<i>At one time. the nine tailed fox drove</i>
<i>the Village Hidden in the Leaves</i>

31
00:02:10.468 --> 00:02:11.935
<i>to the brink of destruction...</i>

32
00:02:15.073 --> 00:02:19.976
<i>That nine tailed monster fox is</i>
<i>sealed within Naruto's body.</i>

33
00:02:22.914 --> 00:02:26.077
- Look at that one.
- <i>Therefore. he's been abhorred</i>

34
00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:28.448
- I hear he's the only one who failed.
- <i>as the Demon Fox by village grown ups.</i>

35
00:02:29.954 --> 00:02:31.251
Serves him right.

36
00:02:31.322 --> 00:02:34.086
Imagine what would happen
if he becomes a Ninja.

37
00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:38.258
Okay. you may open your eyes now.

38
00:02:40.331 --> 00:02:43.198
Congratulations on your graduation.

39
00:02:44.369 --> 00:02:46.360
<i>However. that Naruto.</i>

40
00:02:46.437 --> 00:02:48.428
- Iruka Sensei!
- <i>on my sufferance.</i>

41
00:02:48.506 --> 00:02:50.701
- That hurts!
- <i>graduates from the Ninja Academy.</i>

42
00:02:52.710 --> 00:02:54.507
Say cheese!

43
00:02:55.213 --> 00:02:58.011
<i>He starts off on his first step as a Ninja.</i>

44
00:03:01.319 --> 00:03:04.720
<i>Ninja missions are conducted</i>
<i>by three man cells.</i>

45
00:03:06.157 --> 00:03:07.419
<i>Sasuke Uchiha.</i>

46
00:03:07.959 --> 00:03:09.984
<i>A descendant of the Uchiha clan.</i>

47
00:03:10.061 --> 00:03:12.291
<i>a distinguished family in</i>
<i>Hidden Leaf Village.</i>

48
00:03:12.363 --> 00:03:16.026
<i>He is a boy towards whom Naruto harbors</i>
<i>intense feelings of rivalry.</i>

49
00:03:18.302 --> 00:03:22.932
<i>Sakura Haruno is a Kunoichi who</i>
<i>Naruto has the hots for.</i>

50
00:03:25.109 --> 00:03:30.513
<i>As a Ninja. Naruto carries out missions</i>
<i>with these two rookie Ninjas.</i>

51
00:03:31.916 --> 00:03:34.510
<i>The one who observes and</i>
<i>instructs them.</i>

52
00:03:34.585 --> 00:03:37.986
<i>Kakashi Hatake.</i>
<i>also known as the Copy Ninja.</i>

53
00:03:38.056 --> 00:03:39.785
<i>is Konoha's most skilled Ninja.</i>

54
00:03:44.729 --> 00:03:48.324
<i>One day. Naruto's group takes on</i>
<i>the mission to guard Tazuna.</i>

55
00:03:48.399 --> 00:03:50.833
<i>a master bridge builder</i>
<i>of the Land of Waves.</i>

56
00:03:50.902 --> 00:03:52.802
All right! We're off!

57
00:03:53.004 --> 00:03:57.338
<i>However. Tazuna is targeted by a man</i>
<i>named Gato</i>

58
00:03:57.408 --> 00:04:01.003
<i>who attempts to control</i>
<i>the Land of the Waves.</i>

59
00:04:01.913 --> 00:04:04.211
Stop your darned grumbling!!

60
00:04:07.819 --> 00:04:11.118
- Next time I'll kill him with...
- <i>And Gato had hired a terrifying man</i>

61
00:04:11.189 --> 00:04:13.749
- head chopper!
- <i>for Tazuna's assassination.</i>

62
00:04:14.826 --> 00:04:16.123
<i>Zabuza Momochi...</i>

63
00:04:16.828 --> 00:04:18.921
<i>A Rogue Ninja of the Village Hidden</i>
<i>in the Mist.</i>

64
00:04:18.996 --> 00:04:21.055
<i>He was a man who had excelled at</i>
<i>Silent Killing and</i>

65
00:04:21.132 --> 00:04:24.260
<i>had successfully carried out</i>
<i>many assassinations.</i>

66
00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:32.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

67
00:04:34.078 --> 00:04:35.909
<i>Naruto and the gang have</i>
<i>a tough time of it</i>

68
00:04:35.980 --> 00:04:37.743
<i>in the face of Zabuza's attacks...</i>

69
00:04:42.153 --> 00:04:44.883
Hey! You. with no brows...

70
00:04:45.556 --> 00:04:49.287
Record in your Bingo Book
about the man

71
00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:52.727
who'll one day become
the Leaf Village's Hokage.

72
00:04:54.332 --> 00:04:56.357
Naruto Uzumaki!!

73
00:05:01.572 --> 00:05:02.402
It's not so easy!

74
00:05:06.310 --> 00:05:08.335
<i>A Shuriken in the Shuriken's shadow!</i>

75
00:05:10.715 --> 00:05:13.616
<i>However. the shoe is on the other foot.</i>

76
00:05:13.684 --> 00:05:16.050
<i>thanks to Naruto and Sasuke's</i>
<i>close team work.</i>

77
00:05:22.894 --> 00:05:26.193
<i>Kakashi copies</i>
<i>Zabuza's Jutsu with Sharingan.</i>

78
00:05:26.631 --> 00:05:28.690
- <i>W-What's that?!</i>
- <i>It breaks Zabuza's composure.</i>

79
00:05:31.936 --> 00:05:34.063
<i>Me...?</i>

80
00:05:34.138 --> 00:05:35.400
<i>R-Ridiculous!</i>

81
00:05:36.707 --> 00:05:38.231
<i>Is that his Genjutsu (illusion Jutsu)?</i>

82
00:05:41.345 --> 00:05:43.813
The Water Style! Giant Vortex Jutsu!!

83
00:05:44.549 --> 00:05:45.311
No way!

84
00:06:08.573 --> 00:06:09.369
It's over...

85
00:06:21.219 --> 00:06:23.084
<i>A Tracker Ninja boy</i>
<i>from A Hidden Mist Village</i>

86
00:06:23.154 --> 00:06:25.213
<i>is the one who delivered</i>
<i>the final blow.</i>

87
00:06:26.090 --> 00:06:32.620
I must get rid this corpse
because it contains many secrets.

88
00:06:33.631 --> 00:06:35.724
Now then. please excuse me.

89
00:06:42.840 --> 00:06:44.705
<i>However. this boy. Haku...</i>

90
00:06:44.775 --> 00:06:46.800
<i>was Zabuza's comrade.</i>

91
00:06:47.178 --> 00:06:49.476
Will you be all right the next time?

92
00:06:50.715 --> 00:06:51.841
The next time...

93
00:06:52.984 --> 00:06:55.009
I'll be able to see right
through the Sharingan.

94
00:06:58.155 --> 00:07:00.680
<i>Kakashi who has inferred</i>
<i>that Zabuza is still alive.</i>

95
00:07:00.758 --> 00:07:02.123
<i>gives Naruto and gang...</i>

96
00:07:02.193 --> 00:07:04.184
- Ready!!
- <i>new training in preparation...</i>

97
00:07:04.262 --> 00:07:06.822
- Here I go!
- <i>for Zabuza's second assault.</i>

98
00:07:16.674 --> 00:07:18.369
<i>And then.</i>
<i>One week later...</i>

99
00:07:19.944 --> 00:07:20.933
This mist...

100
00:07:21.379 --> 00:07:23.813
Sasuke! Sakura! They are coming!

101
00:07:27.618 --> 00:07:29.745
This means a rival has emerged. Haku.

102
00:07:30.521 --> 00:07:32.113
So it seems.

103
00:07:34.292 --> 00:07:35.884
<i>The time has come!</i>

104
00:07:37.728 --> 00:07:39.093
Secret Jutsu...

105
00:07:42.533 --> 00:07:44.433
Crystal Ice Mirrors!

106
00:07:50.174 --> 00:07:52.506
Now then... I'll start.

107
00:07:53.711 --> 00:07:55.235
Take <i>this!</i>

108
00:08:30.581 --> 00:08:31.946
Naruto Uzumaki...

109
00:08:32.016 --> 00:08:34.917
is finally here!!

110
00:08:36.354 --> 00:08:39.949
<i>The Number One Hyperactive.</i>
<i>Knucklehead Ninja Joins the Fight!</i>

111
00:08:51.469 --> 00:08:55.303
Now that I've come. you're all right!

112
00:08:55.473 --> 00:08:56.303
Oh...

113
00:08:56.574 --> 00:08:57.404
Naruto!

114
00:08:57.575 --> 00:09:02.444
The hero of a story generally appears
in this kind of situation

115
00:09:02.513 --> 00:09:05.641
and takes out the enemy in no time!

116
00:09:05.983 --> 00:09:08.349
Heh... That brat. eh...

117
00:09:08.719 --> 00:09:10.414
<i>He's long on talk...</i>

118
00:09:11.389 --> 00:09:12.981
<i>Man. that idiot!</i>

119
00:09:13.391 --> 00:09:15.359
<i>Making such a conspicuous entrance...</i>

120
00:09:15.760 --> 00:09:18.354
<i>There's no point if you don't</i>
<i>catch the enemy off guard!</i>

121
00:09:21.165 --> 00:09:22.257
<i>That boy...</i>

122
00:09:27.171 --> 00:09:29.901
<i>What're you doing in a place</i>
<i>like this from morning?</i>

123
00:09:31.242 --> 00:09:32.573
<i>Training!!</i>

124
00:09:33.310 --> 00:09:35.744
<i>Why are you training?</i>

125
00:09:36.213 --> 00:09:38.738
<i>I want to get stronger!</i>

126
00:09:43.387 --> 00:09:47.289
All right. here I go!
Shadow Clone Jutsu...

127
00:09:47.591 --> 00:09:48.615
Huh?!

128
00:09:49.460 --> 00:09:50.256
Oh. no!

129
00:09:50.628 --> 00:09:51.390
Huh?

130
00:09:51.662 --> 00:09:53.061
Get out of the way. Naruto!

131
00:09:57.868 --> 00:09:58.800
Whoa!

132
00:09:58.969 --> 00:09:59.867
What?!

133
00:10:04.175 --> 00:10:05.199
He's saved...

134
00:10:05.276 --> 00:10:08.109
To think the enemy attacks
would cancel each other out...

135
00:10:08.179 --> 00:10:10.272
That was super lucky...

136
00:10:10.347 --> 00:10:12.679
Hey! What're you doing. Naruto?!

137
00:10:12.750 --> 00:10:15.275
Hey! What kind of idiot
would attempt

138
00:10:15.352 --> 00:10:16.842
to cast a Jutsu directly
in front of an opponent?!

139
00:10:17.054 --> 00:10:18.180
What?!

140
00:10:18.756 --> 00:10:22.715
The essence of a Ninja is deception.
How you deceive your opponent.

141
00:10:23.661 --> 00:10:26.824
Even casting one Jutsu.
you avoid the eyes of your opponents.

142
00:10:26.897 --> 00:10:29.991
catch them off balance.
and outsmart them...

143
00:10:31.168 --> 00:10:34.968
The way you made your entrance earlier.
that's just you coming to be a target...

144
00:10:35.406 --> 00:10:38.341
N-Nooo.

145
00:10:38.409 --> 00:10:40.741
But I went to the trouble
of coming to the rescue.

146
00:10:41.679 --> 00:10:43.670
<i>What concerns me more than that is...</i>

147
00:10:49.753 --> 00:10:51.015
<i>That guy...</i>

148
00:10:52.289 --> 00:10:54.780
Haku... What's the idea?

149
00:10:55.759 --> 00:10:58.489
Zabuza. leave this kid to me...

150
00:10:59.296 --> 00:11:02.424
Please let me fight this battle my way.

151
00:11:02.900 --> 00:11:04.231
What did you say?

152
00:11:34.800 --> 00:11:40.204
So you mean no interfering... Haku?

153
00:11:43.442 --> 00:11:46.843
You're naive... as usual...

154
00:11:48.614 --> 00:11:49.706
I'm sorry...

155
00:11:50.816 --> 00:11:51.942
<i>Naive. eh...</i>

156
00:11:52.751 --> 00:11:53.843
<i>True enough...</i>

157
00:11:54.987 --> 00:11:56.386
<i>Judging from these wounds.</i>

158
00:11:56.455 --> 00:11:58.889
<i>there's no mistaking that</i>
<i>I was attacked with a Senbon.</i>

159
00:11:59.491 --> 00:12:02.483
<i>But no vital areas have</i>
<i>been targeted so far.</i>

160
00:12:07.533 --> 00:12:09.433
<i>Does he mean to half kill me?</i>

161
00:12:10.068 --> 00:12:11.467
If so!

162
00:12:12.271 --> 00:12:15.638
As for me. I'll take you out first. so!

163
00:12:18.210 --> 00:12:21.145
<i>It's impossible.</i>
<i>It's too much for Naruto!</i>

164
00:12:21.580 --> 00:12:23.343
<i>I should be the one to...</i>

165
00:12:24.049 --> 00:12:27.212
Hey. Don't get any ideas...

166
00:12:27.986 --> 00:12:29.681
If you move.

167
00:12:29.755 --> 00:12:32.883
you know what'll happen
to that old man. right?

168
00:12:34.459 --> 00:12:35.448
<i>True...</i>

169
00:12:36.128 --> 00:12:39.461
<i>If I move away from here and</i>
<i>head towards Naruto.</i>

170
00:12:40.499 --> 00:12:42.524
<i>Zabuza will kill Tazuna.</i>

171
00:12:43.068 --> 00:12:45.866
<i>No way can Sakura completely</i>
<i>protect him by herself.</i>

172
00:12:46.438 --> 00:12:47.996
How about it?

173
00:12:48.073 --> 00:12:53.204
Let's just see how those young guys
fight against each other.

174
00:12:55.147 --> 00:12:56.546
That mask...

175
00:12:56.615 --> 00:12:59.709
You were Zabuza's comrade. after all.
weren't you!

176
00:13:00.586 --> 00:13:02.918
You've got nerve to deceive us!

177
00:13:04.223 --> 00:13:05.212
I'm sorry.

178
00:13:06.391 --> 00:13:09.417
But. your teacher also said it.
didn't he?

179
00:13:09.795 --> 00:13:13.287
Things like deceiving and
catching one off guard is a Shinobi's duty.

180
00:13:14.099 --> 00:13:16.158
Please don't take it personally.

181
00:13:19.071 --> 00:13:22.040
<i>You don't have that luxury. either!</i>

182
00:13:25.978 --> 00:13:26.672
Huh?

183
00:13:28.914 --> 00:13:29.903
Sasuke?

184
00:13:30.549 --> 00:13:33.848
I haven't... forgotten about you.

185
00:13:35.687 --> 00:13:39.680
<i>Here I thought he had disappeared...</i>
<i>but he was there...</i>

186
00:13:40.792 --> 00:13:45.024
I would rather you had
just gone down quietly.

187
00:13:45.697 --> 00:13:47.562
But it looks like it won't work
that way.

188
00:13:47.766 --> 00:13:50.599
Fine. I'll put an end to it first.

189
00:13:52.004 --> 00:13:53.995
H-Hey!

190
00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:57.936
Naruto. I'll get to you later.

191
00:14:03.315 --> 00:14:05.340
<i>W-What's with him?</i>

192
00:14:06.018 --> 00:14:06.950
<i>This is it!</i>

193
00:14:14.960 --> 00:14:16.621
<i>So the real body is over there. eh...</i>

194
00:14:16.695 --> 00:14:17.525
<i>Okay!</i>

195
00:14:18.030 --> 00:14:19.054
I'm over here.

196
00:14:23.869 --> 00:14:26.667
He moved? How?!

197
00:14:44.323 --> 00:14:46.120
- Sasuke!
- Sasuke!

198
00:14:48.327 --> 00:14:50.227
<i>What was that just now?!</i>

199
00:14:50.295 --> 00:14:53.196
<i>Sasuke's body suddenly got battered...</i>

200
00:14:54.266 --> 00:14:56.393
<i>How's he doing it?!</i>

201
00:15:03.075 --> 00:15:05.066
<i>What kind of Jutsu is he using?</i>

202
00:15:06.011 --> 00:15:09.708
<i>It's conceivable that he has clones</i>
<i>hide in the mirrors and</i>

203
00:15:09.781 --> 00:15:12.215
<i>gets them all to throw</i>
<i>the Senbons simultaneously...</i>

204
00:15:12.351 --> 00:15:14.478
<i>No. they're too fast considering...</i>

205
00:15:14.553 --> 00:15:15.884
<i>What does it mean...</i>

206
00:15:15.954 --> 00:15:17.683
<i>not being able to see even</i>
<i>the trajectory of the weapons?</i>

207
00:15:20.726 --> 00:15:23.786
<i>Also. if it's a mere Clone Jutsu...</i>

208
00:15:24.396 --> 00:15:27.524
<i>I don't see a reason for</i>
<i>these ice mirrors...</i>

209
00:15:30.469 --> 00:15:35.099
<i>In any case. there's no way to question</i>
<i>that these mirrors are pivotal for his attacks.</i>

210
00:15:39.444 --> 00:15:43.278
<i>What I can do is to launch attacks...</i>

211
00:15:43.348 --> 00:15:45.748
<i>from both the outside and inside.</i>

212
00:15:46.051 --> 00:15:48.815
<i>The thing to do is to figure out</i>
<i>the meaning of the mirror!</i>

213
00:15:49.087 --> 00:15:50.884
<i>I'll take care of here!</i>

214
00:15:56.361 --> 00:15:58.192
<i>All there is to do is...</i>

215
00:15:58.463 --> 00:16:03.423
<i>for me to attack the inside and have Naruto</i>
<i>try attacking the mirrors from the outside.</i>

216
00:16:04.136 --> 00:16:06.263
Yo! I came to save you.

217
00:16:08.240 --> 00:16:10.299
You okay. Sasuke?

218
00:16:11.643 --> 00:16:12.575
Oh...

219
00:16:13.245 --> 00:16:16.180
What good will it do you
to catch your ally off guard?

220
00:16:16.314 --> 00:16:18.782
Y-You idiot!

221
00:16:18.850 --> 00:16:21.785
If you're a Shinobi.
you'll move more cautiously!

222
00:16:21.920 --> 00:16:23.353
What's with you?!

223
00:16:23.488 --> 00:16:25.513
I came to the rescue. you know!

224
00:16:25.590 --> 00:16:27.319
If you also come inside the mirrors...

225
00:16:28.527 --> 00:16:31.121
Dang it! I've had it. you fool!

226
00:16:31.229 --> 00:16:33.663
Fool?
What do you mean by fool?!

227
00:16:34.066 --> 00:16:37.058
<i>As to be expected of the</i>
<i>number one unpredictable Ninja.</i>

228
00:16:37.536 --> 00:16:41.472
<i>He is making the situation worse and</i>
<i>worse by coming to aid.</i>

229
00:16:42.140 --> 00:16:44.665
Since it's come to this.
all that is left is to smash the mirrors!

230
00:16:46.078 --> 00:16:46.976
Fire Style!

231
00:16:47.045 --> 00:16:48.842
Hey! What're you going to do?!

232
00:16:48.914 --> 00:16:51.781
These are mirrors made
with freezing water...

233
00:16:51.917 --> 00:16:53.043
If so...

234
00:16:53.118 --> 00:16:54.915
Fireball Jutsu!

235
00:17:08.333 --> 00:17:10.426
It's not working at all!

236
00:17:10.769 --> 00:17:13.738
They won't melt with that
level of firepower.

237
00:17:28.053 --> 00:17:32.547
Darn it! Where'd he attack from?!
Is it the clones?

238
00:17:35.794 --> 00:17:38.024
Where's the real body?!

239
00:17:38.697 --> 00:17:41.165
It's useless for you to even
attempt following with your eyes.

240
00:17:41.399 --> 00:17:43.594
I absolutely will not be caught.

241
00:17:44.102 --> 00:17:46.627
Humph. Shadow Clone Jutsu!

242
00:17:46.705 --> 00:17:47.672
Don't!

243
00:17:49.608 --> 00:17:54.272
If so. I'll find out which is
the real body by hitting them all!

244
00:18:15.867 --> 00:18:21.396
This is a teleportation Jutsu that uses
mirrors that can reflect only my image.

245
00:18:21.973 --> 00:18:23.770
Watching you from the speed I move.

246
00:18:23.842 --> 00:18:26.709
it almost seems as if
you aren't moving at all...

247
00:18:27.846 --> 00:18:28.972
<i>I knew it!</i>

248
00:18:29.447 --> 00:18:31.881
Is that Jutsu... the Kekkei Genkai?!

249
00:18:34.452 --> 00:18:36.477
Kekkei... Genkai?

250
00:18:37.222 --> 00:18:39.622
It's the same type as my Sharingan...

251
00:18:40.659 --> 00:18:44.857
Deep blood ties...
Lineage of paranormal individuals...

252
00:18:45.764 --> 00:18:48.631
A type of Jutsu that is passed on
only through those traits...

253
00:18:48.767 --> 00:18:49.927
Then!

254
00:18:50.335 --> 00:18:51.233
That's right...

255
00:18:51.670 --> 00:18:55.606
It's impossible even for me
to copy that Jutsu...

256
00:18:56.541 --> 00:18:58.509
And there's no way to destroy
that Jutsu. either!

257
00:19:02.981 --> 00:19:04.039
Darn it...

258
00:19:05.517 --> 00:19:08.042
So... what?!

259
00:19:08.853 --> 00:19:11.686
I can't die here yet.

260
00:19:12.157 --> 00:19:15.593
'Cause I have a dream
that I must turn into reality...

261
00:19:15.660 --> 00:19:19.152
The dream to have my strength recognized
by everyone in the village...

262
00:19:19.231 --> 00:19:21.825
and become the Hokage!

263
00:19:23.201 --> 00:19:24.225
<i>Dream...</i>

264
00:19:43.755 --> 00:19:45.450
<i>Pathetic brat.</i>

265
00:19:53.131 --> 00:19:56.828
<i>Brats like you aren't needed</i>
<i>by anyone</i>

266
00:19:56.901 --> 00:20:00.462
<i>and die without ever knowing</i>
<i>any freedom or dreams...</i>

267
00:20:04.142 --> 00:20:07.475
<i>You have the same eyes as I do...</i>

268
00:20:13.518 --> 00:20:17.318
For me. becoming a Shinobi completely
is difficult.

269
00:20:18.490 --> 00:20:21.584
If I can. I don't want to kill you guys...

270
00:20:22.093 --> 00:20:24.584
And I don't want to get killed
by you guys...

271
00:20:25.997 --> 00:20:28.898
But if you guys are
going to come at me...

272
00:20:29.234 --> 00:20:33.170
I'll kill my feelings with a sword and
completely become a Shinobi.

273
00:20:33.872 --> 00:20:38.104
This bridge is the battleground
that connects each of us to our dreams.

274
00:20:39.010 --> 00:20:41.342
I. for the sake of my dream.

275
00:20:41.713 --> 00:20:44.079
And you. for the sake of your dreams.

276
00:20:45.350 --> 00:20:46.840
Please don't hold it against me...

277
00:20:47.986 --> 00:20:50.079
I want to protect the person dear to me...

278
00:20:51.289 --> 00:20:55.453
I work for the sake of that person.
I fight for that person.

279
00:20:55.860 --> 00:20:57.953
and I want to make that
person's dream a reality...

280
00:20:58.363 --> 00:20:59.990
That's my dream.

281
00:21:00.332 --> 00:21:03.460
For the sake of the dream.
I will completely become a Shinobi...

282
00:21:03.835 --> 00:21:06.133
and kill you guys!

283
00:22:52.579 --> 00:22:54.570
Crystal Ice Mirror defeated!

284
00:22:54.648 --> 00:22:57.811
Cuz' I've finally discovered the way
to break through it!

285
00:22:57.885 --> 00:22:59.876
Heh-heh. Okay. Sasuke.

286
00:22:59.953 --> 00:23:03.218
Let's pull out of this place and
go assist Kakashi Sensei.

287
00:23:03.590 --> 00:23:05.649
I've had this bad feeling from
a while ago.

288
00:23:05.726 --> 00:23:10.060
Sensei. Sakura. please hold out somehow
until we get there.

289
00:23:10.864 --> 00:23:14.163
Next episode:
"Zero Visibility: The Sharingan Shatters."

290
00:23:14.234 --> 00:23:16.862
As for me. I'll kick butt once again!

291
00:23:17.305 --> 00:24:17.260
